      <title>银行家们不惜一切代价抢占罕见的收购交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/sanofi-bankers-do-anything-it-takes-to-grab-a-piece-of-rare-french-buyout</link>
